OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FAny low cloud quickly lifting
OL,6,Fand breaking to bring a very warm day
OL,7,Fwith spells of strong sunshine and
OL,8,Flight winds. Fair-weather cloud
OL,9,Fdrifting through at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FClear skies with some patchy
OL,12,Fcloudy to the north. Light winds may
OL,13,Fallow some mist to develop in spots.
OL,14,FFeeling mild with temperatures staying
OL,15,Fabove average.
OL,16,
OL,17,CWednesday:FBright and sunny throughout
OL,18,Fas high cloud moves northwards. Light
OL,19,Fwinds and strong sunshine will allow
OL,20,Ftemperatures to climb into the
OL,21,Fafternoon. Feeling hot in places.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
