OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,6,Ffine few days to come with spells of
OL,7,Fstrong sunshine. Temperatures climbing
OL,8,Fand starting to feel increasingly hot.
OL,9,FStaying dry with light winds.
